quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Boola mbu: “Enywe Abakhayi!"
  109,2,"Shelaamanga shiamulaamanga tawe."
  109,3,"Ne enywe shimulaamanga owelaamanga tawe."
  109,4,"Ne esie shindililaama shiamulaamanga tawe."
  109,5,"Ne enywe shimulaamanga owelaamanga tawe."
  109,6,"Enywe muli nende idini yenyu, nasi endi nende idini yanje.”"
